  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "FAQS",
      "settings": {
        "text_2ddvmUlhUQaZyZT3": "<p>Frequently asked questions</p>",
        "text_S0NHftk2IdryuxVU": "<h3>Does the Carbinox Blaze smartwatch work with Apple iPhone and Android mobile phones or devices?</h3>",
        "text_ZmJalJX4rrP03kAN": "<p>Yes. Blaze pairs over Bluetooth with both iPhone and Android using the Carbinox Pro app.</p>",
        "text_C5vg3OqlyRlfkGIv": "<h3>Can I make or receive calls with the Carbinox Blaze smartwatches?</h3>",
        "text_VjcIdAlGEdITpImg": "<p>Yes. You can make and receive Bluetooth calls from the watch as long as it’s paired to your phone and within range.</p>",
        "text_RvKhtLcvZ06NZ4H2": "<h3>How does the GPS work?</h3>",
        "text_YBm6FIvNOkKZim5V": "<p>To ensure accurate tracking of your activities, the GPS functionality on the Carbinox Blaze works in conjunction with the Carbinox Pro App. When you select any sport mode on your smartwatch, the device relies on your smartphone’s GPS for precise location data. This allows the smartwatch to accurately track your movements, speed, and distance during outdoor activities.</p>",
        "text_ZSZFdx0U0UZlugdA": "<h3>How do I send messages with the AI assistant?</h3>",
        "text_8dY8cZtX50a2JtcZ": "<p></p><p></p><p>Access the Voice Assistant: Simply navigate to the voice assistant feature on your Carbinox Blaze smartwatch by selecting it from the main menu.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>Activate Voice Commands: Once in the voice assistant menu, tap the screen to speak.</p></li><li><p>Send a Text Message: After activating the assistant, you can send a text message by saying the command, for example, “Send a text message to [name] saying [message].”</p></li><li><p>Message Sent: The AI assistant will instantly pair with your smartphone and send the message as instructed.</p></li><li><p>You can also make calls with the AI voice assistant. Just follow the same steps as the ones to send a message but instead, say \"Call [name]\".</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Important Disclaimer:</strong></p><p>While the AI voice assistant is highly responsive, it is also very sensitive. This means that in some cases, the message may not be delivered exactly as you intended. Always double-check your command to ensure it’s understood correctly. We recommend speaking clearly and confirming any important messages. </p>",
        "text_WWrUUPLTWkZ8KwIq": "<h3>Does it support third-party music apps like Spotify and Pandora?</h3>",
        "text_A8aCDnzzkL5ewcsk": "<p>Blaze can control music playing on your phone (play / pause / skip) for supported apps, but it doesn’t install or stream Spotify, Pandora, or other music apps directly on the watch.</p>",
        "text_Rp8iVxO23xfSelZ2": "<h3>How long does the Carbinox Blaze smartwatch battery last?</h3>",
        "text_k6KSUsmJ3XziisSK": "<p>Under normal use, the Blaze battery can last up to about 14 days on a single charge, and it takes roughly 90 minutes to fully recharge.</p>",
        "text_SsA5II0ZHsz9wyM4": "<h3>Is the Carbinox Blaze smartwatch waterproof? If so, how deep can it go?</h3>",
        "text_s74iX2z8SitbbdOT": "<p>Blaze is rated IP69K and 5 ATM, which means it’s dust-tight, handles high-pressure water, and is safe for swimming and general water use down to 50 meters.</p>",
        "text_kcQtIwq3m7nBZLVh": "<h3>What if my Carbinox Blaze breaks or fails?</h3>",
        "text_LvbmrM7Kfa3XYjUO": "<p>If your Carbinox Blaze fails or even breaks under regular use, you’re covered with our Lifetime Warranty. Meaning, we’ll send you a replacement for 100% for FREE. That’s how confident we are about the quality and durability of our smartwatches.</p>",
        "text_mVTUYZtlDMY2ELy6": "<h3>Do you offer a money-back guarantee?</h3>",
        "text_iM63KNUcgObowHFx": "<p>Yes we do! You have 45 days to try our product and if it doesn’t meet your expectations, you can return it and get 100% of your money back, no questions asked! You’re basically trying it for free.</p>",
        "text_dwHdHUYmmqJlGZJN": "<h3>Why doesn&apos;t the Carbinox Blaze smartwatch package include a power adapter?</h3>",
        "text_qde0ETpz0jY2U9O6": "<p>The watch comes with its own magnetic charging cable that plugs into any standard USB port. A separate wall adapter isn’t included so you can use whatever charger or power source you already have and avoid extra waste.</p>",
        "text_Ce3geUi4NJ4L7IZD": "<h3>My Carbinox Blaze smartwatch&apos;s Bluetooth keeps disconnecting from my mobile device, how do I fix this?</h3>",
        "text_BfjdkXXFLVJ6dJsw": "<p>If your Carbinox Blaze smartwatch&apos;s Bluetooth keeps disconnecting from your mobile device, please ensure that both the Carbinox app and your device&apos;s operating system are up to date. Restart your smartwatch, then try reconnecting via Bluetooth. If the problem persists, consider performing a factory reset on your watch. For further assistance, contact support at <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"mailto:info@shopcarbinox.com\">info@shopcarbinox.com</a>.</p>"
      }
    }
